1
00:00:33,554 --> 00:00:36,224
AKU AKAN SEGERA MENGHAMPIRIMU

2
00:00:37,642 --> 00:00:39,268
<i>Ini terlalu kejam.</i>

3
00:00:40,853 --> 00:00:42,939
<i>Hanya karena kupu-kupu sialan itu,</i>

4
00:00:44,857 --> 00:00:46,692
<i>aku terpaksa bersembunyi</i>...

5
00:00:49,278 --> 00:00:50,988
<i>dan menderita selama ini.</i>

6
00:01:03,334 --> 00:01:04,877
<i>Tapi kenapa…</i>

7
00:01:06,837 --> 00:01:08,798
<i>kupu-kupu itu harus ibunya?</i>

8
00:01:19,267 --> 00:01:20,434
<i>Mun-yeong…</i>

9
00:01:23,312 --> 00:01:25,189
<i>Aku sangat berharap...</i>

10
00:01:27,566 --> 00:01:29,777
<i>dia tidak mengetahui kenyataannya.</i>

11
00:01:31,654 --> 00:01:33,239
<i>Aku tidak mau dia terluka.</i>

12
00:01:35,950 --> 00:01:39,787
<i>Aku tak mau dia memedulikan</i>
<i>perasaan orang lain.</i>

13
00:01:42,248 --> 00:01:44,166
<i>Seperti tong kosong...</i>

14
00:01:45,293 --> 00:01:47,128
<i>yang tak merasakan apa pun.</i>

15
00:01:51,966 --> 00:01:53,259
<i>Aku merasa bersalah...</i>

16
00:01:54,552 --> 00:01:58,097
<i>kepada Sang-tae dan ibuku.</i>

17
00:02:27,543 --> 00:02:28,753
Kami berangkat.

18
00:02:30,212 --> 00:02:32,131
Kau bisa menyusul jika berubah pikiran.

19
00:02:40,890 --> 00:02:41,974
GANG-TAE

20
00:02:42,058 --> 00:02:45,186
ALAMAT STUDIO FOTO

21
00:03:55,923 --> 00:03:58,175
<i>Aku sudah tidak bermimpi buruk lagi</i>

22
00:03:58,843 --> 00:04:00,511
<i>berkat Mang-tae yang kau berikan.</i>

23
00:04:01,720 --> 00:04:04,598
<i>Aku senang bisa memiliki keluarga</i>

24
00:04:05,808 --> 00:04:09,687
<i>seperti kau, Sang-tae, Mang-tae.</i>

25
00:04:19,321 --> 00:04:20,322
<i>Catatan kecil.</i>

26
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:23,534
<i>Tolong kembalikan Mang-tae.</i>

27
00:04:23,617 --> 00:04:24,618
<i>Dia milikku.</i>

28
00:05:28,265 --> 00:05:30,309
Bu, silakan duduk di kursi.

29
00:05:30,392 --> 00:05:32,520
Pak, silakan berdiri di samping kursi.

30
00:05:33,562 --> 00:05:35,898
Bagus sekali.
Pak, tolong bergeser lebih dekat.

31
00:05:36,315 --> 00:05:38,067
- Ya.
- Bagus sekali.

32
00:05:38,484 --> 00:05:40,903
Lihat ke arah kamera.

33
00:05:40,986 --> 00:05:44,240
Senyum lebih lebar. Senyumlah.
Lihat ke arah kamera.

34
00:05:44,990 --> 00:05:46,700
- Satu, dua…
- Lihat!

35
00:05:46,784 --> 00:05:48,369
Tunggu sebentar.

36
00:05:50,329 --> 00:05:52,832
Adikku... Adikku datang.

37
00:05:53,082 --> 00:05:57,753
Adikku... Adik kandungku.

38
00:06:36,917 --> 00:06:37,793
Aku belum...

39
00:06:39,753 --> 00:06:40,880
terlambat, 'kan?

40
00:06:54,518 --> 00:06:57,605
Jika tak datang, aku berniat menyunting
dan memasukkanmu ke foto.

41
00:06:59,523 --> 00:07:00,774
Makanya aku datang.

42
00:07:00,858 --> 00:07:03,652
Keren sekali. Kau terlihat keren.

43
00:07:03,736 --> 00:07:05,654
Berapa harga jas ini? 100.000 won?

44
00:07:07,031 --> 00:07:09,241
- Kau juga keren.
- Ya. Aku memang keren.

45
00:07:09,325 --> 00:07:11,535
Kau menata rambutmu gel.

46
00:07:11,619 --> 00:07:13,287
Kau memakai gel milikku?

47
00:07:13,370 --> 00:07:15,372
Jika kalian bertiga
ingin dipotret bersama,

48
00:07:15,456 --> 00:07:17,082
tolong berdiri sejajar.

49
00:07:17,166 --> 00:07:19,877
Ya. Kami bertiga dipotret bersama.

50
00:07:19,960 --> 00:07:23,339
Ini foto keluarga kami. Foto keluarga.

51
00:07:23,422 --> 00:07:25,341
Bapak sekalian, mohon lebih merapat.

52
00:07:37,478 --> 00:07:40,105
Karena foto keluarga,
tolong dibuat lebih ceria.

53
00:07:40,189 --> 00:07:41,315
Aku akan mulai memotret.

54
00:07:42,066 --> 00:07:42,900
Tersenyum.

55
00:07:43,359 --> 00:07:44,360
Baiklah.

56
00:07:44,860 --> 00:07:47,696
Satu, dua, tiga.

57
00:07:52,701 --> 00:07:58,290
BAB 13
AYAH DARI KISAH DUA BERSAUDARA

58
00:08:04,421 --> 00:08:07,007
Aku sudah kembali.

59
00:08:11,595 --> 00:08:14,390
- Halo, Pak Lee.
- Seung-jae.

60
00:08:15,766 --> 00:08:17,142
Kau mau pergi ke mana?

61
00:08:18,018 --> 00:08:19,269
Aku mengirimkanmu SMS.

62
00:08:19,353 --> 00:08:22,147
Aku mau menemani Penulis Ko
dan Ilustrator Moon untuk riset

63
00:08:22,231 --> 00:08:23,148
di perpustakan seni.

64
00:08:23,232 --> 00:08:25,109
Hei! Bagaimana aku tahu?

65
00:08:25,192 --> 00:08:26,819
Kau menyuruhku mematikan ponsel.

66
00:08:26,902 --> 00:08:27,820
Aduh!

67
00:08:27,903 --> 00:08:29,863
Ju-ri ada di dalam kamar!

68
00:08:35,786 --> 00:08:37,996
Sepertinya rencana kita berhasil.

69
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:39,081
Benarkah?

70
00:08:39,832 --> 00:08:44,336
Jadi, sebelum Ju-ri bertanya
mengenai kencan buta,

71
00:08:44,420 --> 00:08:47,214
jangan pernah membahasnya
terlebih dahulu. Kau mengerti?

72
00:08:47,631 --> 00:08:48,465
Kenapa?

73
00:08:48,632 --> 00:08:51,135
Bukankah kau berbohong
soal aku bertemu wanita

74
00:08:51,218 --> 00:08:52,386
yang mirip Song Hye-kyo?

75
00:08:52,469 --> 00:08:54,304
Lakukan saja sesuai kataku.

76
00:08:54,388 --> 00:08:56,640
Aku harus pergi. Aku pamit.

77
00:08:56,724 --> 00:08:57,808
Ya. Hati-hati di jalan.

78
00:09:04,064 --> 00:09:05,190
Baiklah.

79
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:09,319
Ju-ri.

80
00:09:10,195 --> 00:09:11,572
Bolehkah aku masuk?

81
00:09:13,991 --> 00:09:14,825
Ya.

82
00:09:23,333 --> 00:09:25,627
Aku ingin lapor bahwa aku sudah kembali.

83
00:09:26,545 --> 00:09:28,756
Kau pasti lelah. Istirahatlah.

84
00:09:33,510 --> 00:09:34,928
Kau libur hari ini?

85
00:09:35,012 --> 00:09:36,054
Ya.

86
00:09:39,308 --> 00:09:42,519
Aku membawa daun murbai musiman

87
00:09:42,603 --> 00:09:45,314
dan kimchi <i>godeulppaegi</i>
yang disiapkan ibuku.

88
00:09:45,397 --> 00:09:47,232
Jika belum makan, maukah kau…

89
00:09:47,316 --> 00:09:49,193
Aku sudah makan. Selamat menikmati.

90
00:09:51,111 --> 00:09:51,945
Baik.

91
00:10:00,621 --> 00:10:01,789
Aku habis berkencan.

92
00:10:03,082 --> 00:10:03,916
Aku tahu.

93
00:10:03,999 --> 00:10:06,627
Dia sangat mirip Song Hye-kyo.

94
00:10:06,710 --> 00:10:07,753
Sejak pertemuan pertama

95
00:10:07,836 --> 00:10:10,547
suasananya bagus
karena dia tipe wanita idamanku…

96
00:10:10,631 --> 00:10:11,882
Pak Lee.

97
00:10:11,965 --> 00:10:13,175
Aku harus pelajari materi

98
00:10:13,258 --> 00:10:15,219
untuk pelatihan besok.

99
00:10:17,012 --> 00:10:19,640
Baiklah. Maafkan aku.

100
00:10:20,808 --> 00:10:22,768
Belajarlah dengan giat. Semangat!

101
00:10:40,452 --> 00:10:43,455
Sial. Aku sembrono sekali.

102
00:10:47,751 --> 00:10:49,670
Semuanya jadi kacau.

103
00:11:00,514 --> 00:11:02,850
SERIUS? SONG HYE-KYO? KAU SENANG?

104
00:11:18,156 --> 00:11:19,074
Mun-yeong sialan.

105
00:11:19,324 --> 00:11:22,160
Dia pikir bisa seenaknya membatalkan?

106
00:11:28,584 --> 00:11:29,459
Tidak apa-apa.

107
00:11:29,543 --> 00:11:31,879
Keluarkan saja agar tak menjadi penyakit.

108
00:11:32,421 --> 00:11:34,256
Semoga panjang umur, Seung-jae.

109
00:11:35,299 --> 00:11:36,592
Ya.

110
00:11:37,176 --> 00:11:40,262
Halo, Penata Artistik Yoo Seung-jae.

111
00:11:41,930 --> 00:11:44,766
Kau mengenakan jas. Keren sekali!

112
00:11:47,519 --> 00:11:50,606
- Kau selalu ingin ke sini.
- Ya. Perpustakaan seni.

113
00:11:50,689 --> 00:11:52,733
Di sini ada banyak buku bergambar.

114
00:11:52,816 --> 00:11:54,359
- Ikuti aku.
- Ya.

115
00:11:54,443 --> 00:11:55,319
Sebelah sini.

116
00:11:56,528 --> 00:11:57,571
- Ayo.
- Kau.

117
00:11:58,614 --> 00:12:00,866
- Mulai sekarang jangan pakai jas.
- Kenapa?

118
00:12:00,949 --> 00:12:01,909
Tidak bagus.

119
00:12:02,701 --> 00:12:04,912
Seragam perawat jauh lebih cocok untukmu.

120
00:12:05,120 --> 00:12:06,163
Begitu?

121
00:12:06,872 --> 00:12:08,415
Aku berniat beli beberapa setelan.

122
00:12:09,708 --> 00:12:10,834
Ternyata nyaman dipakai.

123
00:12:10,918 --> 00:12:12,544
Tak nyaman dilihat. Jangan dipakai.

124
00:12:12,628 --> 00:12:13,545
Baiklah.

125
00:12:14,338 --> 00:12:15,589
Kau juga jangan pakai itu

126
00:12:16,757 --> 00:12:18,133
karena tak nyaman dilihat.

127
00:12:19,426 --> 00:12:20,427
Sialan.

128
00:12:20,510 --> 00:12:22,638
Hei! Aku bilang jangan pakai jas lagi!

129
00:12:22,721 --> 00:12:24,973
Atau aku akan merobeknya!

130
00:12:25,057 --> 00:12:26,391
Jangan dipakai!

131
00:12:27,434 --> 00:12:30,854
"Dia memiliki rumah boneka.

132
00:12:30,938 --> 00:12:34,232
Rumah boneka itu sangat indah."

133
00:12:34,316 --> 00:12:39,029
Seniman ini adalah ilustrator
yang sangat terkenal.

134
00:12:39,112 --> 00:12:41,031
Di kalangan anak-anak,

135
00:12:41,114 --> 00:12:42,866
- gaya melukis ini…
- Perpustakaan…

136
00:12:42,950 --> 00:12:44,785
Di dalam perpustakan tak boleh berisik.

137
00:12:44,868 --> 00:12:46,703
Itu etika yang benar.

138
00:12:46,787 --> 00:12:48,789
PIRING EMAS

139
00:12:51,291 --> 00:12:52,459
Seperti yang kau tahu,

140
00:12:52,542 --> 00:12:56,129
tulisan Penulis Ko
cenderung kejam dan tajam.

141
00:12:56,505 --> 00:13:00,175
Aku ingin kau mengurangi
kesan yang tajam itu

142
00:13:00,258 --> 00:13:03,095
dengan kehangatan dan keluguan.

143
00:13:03,929 --> 00:13:08,183
Misalnya seperti kabut pagi
saat musim semi.

144
00:13:08,266 --> 00:13:09,643
Juga…

145
00:13:09,726 --> 00:13:13,647
Gunakan warna-warna pastel
yang lembut dan ramah

146
00:13:13,730 --> 00:13:17,109
untuk menetralkan ketajaman
dari tulisan Penulis Ko…

147
00:13:17,192 --> 00:13:18,026
Aku menolak.

148
00:13:18,986 --> 00:13:20,570
- Aku tak mau.
- Apa?

149
00:13:21,154 --> 00:13:21,989
Kenapa?

150
00:13:22,280 --> 00:13:25,951
Jika dinetralkan akan menjadi tawar,
tidak ada rasanya.

151
00:13:26,034 --> 00:13:28,036
Tidak akan ada yang suka.

152
00:13:28,412 --> 00:13:29,705
Bahkan anjing pun tak suka.

153
00:13:31,373 --> 00:13:32,374
Dia keren sekali.

154
00:13:32,874 --> 00:13:34,751
ANJING MUSIM SEMI

155
00:13:42,968 --> 00:13:44,594
DAHULU KALA, HIDUP SEEJOR ANJING…

156
00:13:48,682 --> 00:13:50,142
Kau mirip Anjing Musim Semi.

157
00:13:53,103 --> 00:13:53,937
Kenapa begitu?

158
00:13:54,021 --> 00:13:56,857
Temanmu. Jae-su atau Jae-min?

159
00:13:57,274 --> 00:13:58,567
Dia yang memberitahuku.

160
00:13:59,693 --> 00:14:02,654
Kau selalu menyembunyikan perasaanmu

161
00:14:02,738 --> 00:14:04,448
dan menangis sendirian.

162
00:14:06,533 --> 00:14:07,743
Seperti Anjing Musim Semi.

163
00:14:10,954 --> 00:14:12,164
Kalian berdua bertemu?

164
00:14:12,706 --> 00:14:15,000
Aku memanggilnya ke rumah

165
00:14:15,083 --> 00:14:16,752
untuk menanyakan alasanmu marah.

166
00:14:18,920 --> 00:14:21,465
Aku pesan sepuluh kotak piza,
dia datang dalam sekejap.

167
00:14:24,259 --> 00:14:25,260
Lalu?

168
00:14:26,344 --> 00:14:27,179
Apa katanya?

169
00:14:28,930 --> 00:14:30,348
Jangan cari tahu lebih lanjut.

170
00:14:31,350 --> 00:14:33,852
Percuma memaksa mencari tahu perasaanmu.

171
00:14:36,938 --> 00:14:38,356
Aku sudah merelakannya.

172
00:14:39,441 --> 00:14:40,817
Aku tak penasaran lagi.

173
00:14:45,572 --> 00:14:46,573
Ko Mun-yeong.

174
00:14:54,456 --> 00:14:55,332
Aku…

175
00:14:58,543 --> 00:15:00,670
sudah sangat muak dan lelah

176
00:15:02,005 --> 00:15:03,173
melindungi...

177
00:15:04,341 --> 00:15:05,509
dan merawat orang lain.

178
00:15:07,177 --> 00:15:09,012
Aku melakukannya dengan terpaksa

179
00:15:09,596 --> 00:15:11,473
karena itulah alasanku dilahirkan...

180
00:15:13,600 --> 00:15:15,185
dan caraku mencari uang.

181
00:15:18,146 --> 00:15:18,980
Tapi?

182
00:15:22,651 --> 00:15:23,860
Aku mau mengubah...

183
00:15:25,987 --> 00:15:27,239
kewajiban itu...

184
00:15:30,492 --> 00:15:32,369
menjadi tujuan hidupku.

185
00:15:35,205 --> 00:15:37,165
Setelah kupikirkan...

186
00:15:38,875 --> 00:15:40,085
melindungi keluarga itu...

187
00:15:41,670 --> 00:15:43,922
ternyata keren dan luar biasa.

188
00:15:46,675 --> 00:15:48,301
Aku tak akan membiarkan siapa pun

189
00:15:49,344 --> 00:15:50,637
mengganggu keluargaku.

190
00:15:52,597 --> 00:15:53,849
Jika keluargaku direbut,

191
00:15:55,183 --> 00:15:57,018
akan kukejar sampai ketemu.

192
00:15:59,688 --> 00:16:02,399
Aku pasti melindungi keluargaku.

193
00:16:09,322 --> 00:16:10,574
Apa aku termasuk...

194
00:16:16,621 --> 00:16:17,956
keluarga itu?

195
00:16:19,958 --> 00:16:21,501
Kita sudah berfoto bersama.

196
00:16:30,802 --> 00:16:31,678
Kita keluarga.

197
00:16:47,360 --> 00:16:50,780
RUMAH SAKIT JIWA OK

198
00:16:51,448 --> 00:16:53,450
Jangan pernah menghubungiku lagi.

199
00:16:56,119 --> 00:16:57,913
Kau tak berhak kemari.

200
00:16:59,289 --> 00:17:00,790
Silakan! Datang saja.

201
00:17:00,874 --> 00:17:02,876
Aku akan membunuhmu nanti.

202
00:17:10,759 --> 00:17:12,594
Jika dia menghubungiku lagi,

203
00:17:13,261 --> 00:17:15,180
cukup katakan aku sudah mati.

204
00:17:22,020 --> 00:17:23,730
Bu Seon-hae. Tunggu.

205
00:17:24,189 --> 00:17:25,732
Mari berjalan-jalan di taman.

206
00:17:25,815 --> 00:17:27,067
Siapa yang menelepon?

207
00:17:27,150 --> 00:17:29,986
Orang itu lagi. Ayahnya Bu Seon-hae.

208
00:17:31,279 --> 00:17:32,364
Tak punya malu.

209
00:17:32,697 --> 00:17:35,659
Kudengar dia dibuang ke rumah dukun
dan dianggap kerasukan.

210
00:17:35,742 --> 00:17:38,328
Aku juga tak mau bertemu ayah seperti itu.

211
00:17:38,578 --> 00:17:40,372
Ke mana saja dia selama ini?

212
00:17:41,122 --> 00:17:43,041
- Perawat Sun Byeol.
- Ya?

213
00:17:43,625 --> 00:17:45,168
Kau tak boleh sembarangan

214
00:17:45,252 --> 00:17:46,461
membahas keluarga pasien.

215
00:17:47,712 --> 00:17:49,839
Jangan hanya menilai dari satu sisi.

216
00:17:50,590 --> 00:17:52,509
Orang tua pasti punya alasannya sendiri.

217
00:17:53,552 --> 00:17:54,511
Baik.

218
00:18:03,770 --> 00:18:05,647
Ya. Aku selalu salah.

219
00:18:06,231 --> 00:18:09,150
TAK MASALAH, KAU PASTI BISA
PEDOMAN KATAK UNTUK MENCOBA LAGI

220
00:18:09,693 --> 00:18:10,694
Ya.

221
00:18:13,697 --> 00:18:15,323
- Astaga. Bu.
- Halo.

222
00:18:16,324 --> 00:18:17,158
Aduh.

223
00:18:17,534 --> 00:18:19,578
Kenapa kau tak makan malam?

224
00:18:19,661 --> 00:18:21,621
- Itu…
- Kenapa?

225
00:18:21,705 --> 00:18:24,374
- Silakan duduk di sini.
- Ya.

226
00:18:24,874 --> 00:18:27,711
Ada yang harus kukerjakan.

227
00:18:29,170 --> 00:18:30,171
Begitu.

228
00:18:31,256 --> 00:18:32,924
Astaga. Tak perlu melakukan itu!

229
00:18:34,009 --> 00:18:36,636
Kau tak akan bisa tidur jika kelaparan.
Makanlah ini.

230
00:18:37,637 --> 00:18:38,555
Terima kasih.

231
00:18:44,602 --> 00:18:47,188
Orang dewasa yang membaca dongeng

232
00:18:47,731 --> 00:18:50,108
terlihat polos dan keren.

233
00:18:50,942 --> 00:18:53,903
Tidak begitu. Ini pekerjaanku.

234
00:18:54,404 --> 00:18:56,197
- Aku makan.
- Ya, silakan.

235
00:19:01,953 --> 00:19:03,163
Enak sekali.

236
00:19:05,832 --> 00:19:09,085
Sejujurnya aku sangat lapar,

237
00:19:10,587 --> 00:19:12,339
tapi tak bisa makan karena malu.

238
00:19:13,506 --> 00:19:15,008
Kenapa kau malu?

239
