01:18:54,678 --> 01:18:55,554
Mun-yeong.

981
01:18:56,138 --> 01:18:57,890
Katakan itu tak benar!

982
01:20:51,295 --> 01:20:52,129
<i>Mun-yeong…</i>

983
01:20:53,714 --> 01:20:55,507
