986
01:20:59,511 --> 01:21:01,472
<i>Aku yakin tadi di sini.</i>

987
01:21:02,556 --> 01:21:03,557
<i>Sang-tae.</i>

988
01:21:03,640 --> 01:21:04,892
<i>Aku takut.</i>

989
01:21:06,226 --> 01:21:09,438
Aku akan melindungimu. Aku kakakmu.

990
01:21:09,730 --> 01:21:11,023
<i>Aku walimu.</i>

991
01:21:12,232 --> 01:21:13,400
<i>Mendekatlah.</i>

992
01:21:14,443 --> 01:21:15,778
Ibu.

993
01:21:15,861 --> 01:21:17,571
Maafkan aku.

994
01:21:17,654 --> 01:21:18,781
<i>- Hentikan!</i>
<i>- Mun-yeong.</i>

995
01:21:18,864 --> 01:21:20,115
